title: Stoneblock2禁止地狱
txt_content: Stoneblock2地狱不能去了是什么模组禁用了地狱啊

replies.author: 九耀龙翔
replies.txt_content:
Stoneblock Dimensions
https://www.curseforge.com/minec ... oneblock-dimensions
专门为整合包写的mod
This mod adds new stoneblock versions of mining and end dimension, and disables the vanilla End and nether, these new dims are access by traveling to set y-level
禁用原版末地和地狱，增加“mining”和“end”两个纬度，新纬度通过不同的y值来传送
